Interface CSVUtilsInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
CSVUtilsController
public interface CSVUtilsInterface
Interface defining methods for CSV data handling in the Hospital Management System. Provides methods to manage data for staff, patients, medicines, appointments, and more.
